translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エリアを越えるとみんな裸になる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When crossing the area, everyone becomes naked.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: スシヌはエールにひっつく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sushinu clings to Yell.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女達の裸、何かイベント
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The women's naked bodies, some kind of event.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 裸迷宮を進んでいる、裸の二人が現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Advancing through the naked labyrinth, two naked people appear.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アトランタとジュノー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Atlanta and Juno.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とにもニコニコうれしそう、裸の良さが世界に広まる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Everyone is smiling happily; the appeal of being naked is spreading throughout the world.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 君達の身体はと裸を批評始める・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They begin to criticize your bodies and nakedness...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うっとおしぃのでさっさと倒します
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Since they're annoying, I'll quickly defeat them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞戦闘
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Battle

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: オーブを見つけ取得します。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You find and obtain an orb.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここで引き返してもいいが、この事件をそのままに出来ないと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You could turn back here, but you can't leave this incident unresolved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エールは先に進む事を決断
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yell decides to proceed forward.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 裸族王バファムーンが居る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The naked tribe king Bafamoon is here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パセリが魔法のランプについてきく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Parsley asks about the magic lamp.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 確かにその通りだ、この魔法ランプにより現れた神バンオペタにより
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's true; it was by the god Banopeta who appeared through this magic lamp.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私は天恵を頂いたのだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have received a heavenly blessing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それは危険な間違ったものですと言っても聞いてもらえない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if I tell him it is a dangerous mistake, he won't listen.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 話をしている最中、エールの後ろで隠れているスシヌを見てバファムーンが叱る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While talking, Bafamoon scolds Sushinu who is hiding behind Yell.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そこの娘、裸を隠すとはなにごと、それはやましい心、自分がよく見られたいという心があるから
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hey girl, why are you hiding your nakedness? That's a guilty heart, a desire to be seen well by others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: くいあらためよと説教
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He preaches that you should repent.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンスの記憶もあっても怯えるスシヌ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sushinu, frightened even with memories of Zansu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それをエールが庇う、ひとそれぞれ強要するなと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yell defends her, saying not to force others individually.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞戦闘
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Battle

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 裸族王バファムーンは倒れた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The naked tribe king Bafamoon has been defeated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それにともない、裸エリアは消えて行った。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Along with that, the naked area disappeared.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: みんな服を着て一安心。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Everyone put on clothes and felt relieved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パセリは魔法のランプを取るが、ランプは砕けて消えた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Parsley takes the magic lamp, but it shatters and vanishes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そして、バンオペタの証Ｂ　を拾う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Then, they pick up the Proof B of Banopeta.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旅立つエール達を見つめる母親達
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mothers watch Yell and the others as they depart.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あれから２週間、今度はヘルマンに向かった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Two weeks later, they head toward Helman.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いろいろな冒険の様子
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Scenes of various adventures.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: Ｒの紋章を使って道行く人に試してみたが出なかった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They tried using the R emblem on passersby, but it didn't appear.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 街道を移動中
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Moving along the highway.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 東ヘルマンに関する話題
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A topic regarding East Helman.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 反ランスの国、自分達を襲ったデフェンダーの母国
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The anti-Rance country, the motherland of the Defenders who attacked them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もし自分達がランスを倒したらどうなるのかな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What would happen if they defeated Rance?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスを元に戻しても彼らは納得しない、火だねは残る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if Rance is restored, they won't be satisfied; the spark of conflict remains.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンス、リアがわざと残している話
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The story that Zansu and Ria are deliberately leaving it unresolved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 西ヘルマン首都に到着
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arrival at West Helman capital.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 貧乏だけで温和な国、魔物界の一部も持っており、魔物、人間などで共存している。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A poor but peaceful country, partly part of the monster world, coexisting with monsters and humans.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シーラが大統領
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sheila is the president.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 貴方たちの話は聞いているわ、でも、ごめんなさい。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have heard your story, but I'm sorry.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ついレリコフにオーブの事を話てしまった、あの子ったらヒーロー君を連れて先に取ってくると
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I accidentally told Relikov about the orb; that kid took Hero-kun and went ahead to get it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 向かってしまったの・・　みんなが来てから一緒に行くべきなのに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They went... We should have gone together after everyone arrived.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 場所はシベリア、巨大戦艦内
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Location: Siberia, inside a giant battleship.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すごい寒いシベリアに来ます、始めて
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Coming to the very cold Siberia, for the first time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 目的を再確認
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reconfirming the objectives.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・レリコフ、ヒーローと会う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: - Meet with Relikov and Hero.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・巨大戦艦でオーブを取る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: - Retrieve the orb on the giant battleship.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 氷雪地帯を移動中、キャラバンを発見
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While traveling through the snowy region, they discover a caravan.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 少し寄ってみる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They stop by briefly.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 世界一と言われる移動型売春宿。有名です。高いので一般では利用出来ないが、サービス満点
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A mobile brothel said to be the best in the world. Famous and expensive, so not accessible to the general public, but offers excellent service.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここから少年達のエロ話になります。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: From here, it turns into an erotic story involving the boys.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンス　俺はそこで筆おろしをするつもりだったのだ、一緒にどうだとか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Zansu: I intended to lose my virginity there, inviting someone to join me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女性向けのサービスもあるらしいよ、最高のサービスでやさしく処女を捨てさせてくれんだって
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Apparently, they also have services for women, offering the best care to gently help them lose their virginity.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの子供達は、みんな童貞と処女
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance's children are all virgins, both boys and girls.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エールが男か女かで　ボーイズトークかガールズトーク
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Depending on whether Yell is male or female, it's boys' talk or girls' talk.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もちろん、今はいかない。立ち去ります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Of course, they don't go now. They leave.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シベリアを進んでいると・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As they advance through Siberia...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 向こうに誰かがいる、こっちに向かって走ってくる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Someone is over there, running toward them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エリアを越えるとみんな裸になる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When crossing the area, everyone becomes naked.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: スシヌはエールにひっつく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sushinu clings to Yell.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女達の裸、何かイベント
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The women's naked bodies, some kind of event.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 裸迷宮を進んでいる、裸の二人が現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Advancing through the naked labyrinth, two naked people appear.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アトランタとジュノー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Atlanta and Juno.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とにもニコニコうれしそう、裸の良さが世界に広まる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Everyone is smiling happily; the appeal of being naked is spreading throughout the world.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 君達の身体はと裸を批評始める・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They begin to criticize your bodies and nakedness...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うっとおしぃのでさっさと倒します
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Since they're annoying, I'll quickly defeat them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞戦闘
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Battle

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: オーブを見つけ取得します。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You find and obtain an orb.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここで引き返してもいいが、この事件をそのままに出来ないと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You could turn back here, but you can't leave this incident unresolved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エールは先に進む事を決断
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yell decides to proceed forward.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 裸族王バファムーンが居る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The naked tribe king Bafamoon is here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パセリが魔法のランプについてきく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Parsley asks about the magic lamp.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 確かにその通りだ、この魔法ランプにより現れた神バンオペタにより
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's true; it was by the god Banopeta who appeared through this magic lamp.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私は天恵を頂いたのだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have received a heavenly blessing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それは危険な間違ったものですと言っても聞いてもらえない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if I tell him it is a dangerous mistake, he won't listen.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 話をしている最中、エールの後ろで隠れているスシヌを見てバファムーンが叱る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While talking, Bafamoon scolds Sushinu who is hiding behind Yell.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そこの娘、裸を隠すとはなにごと、それはやましい心、自分がよく見られたいという心があるから
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hey girl, why are you hiding your nakedness? That's a guilty heart, a desire to be seen well by others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: くいあらためよと説教
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He preaches that you should repent.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンスの記憶もあっても怯えるスシヌ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sushinu, frightened even with memories of Zansu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それをエールが庇う、ひとそれぞれ強要するなと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yell defends her, saying not to force others individually.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞戦闘
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Battle

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 裸族王バファムーンは倒れた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The naked tribe king Bafamoon has been defeated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それにともない、裸エリアは消えて行った。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Along with that, the naked area disappeared.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: みんな服を着て一安心。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Everyone put on clothes and felt relieved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パセリは魔法のランプを取るが、ランプは砕けて消えた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Parsley takes the magic lamp, but it shatters and vanishes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そして、バンオペタの証Ｂ　を拾う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Then, they pick up the Proof B of Banopeta.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旅立つエール達を見つめる母親達
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mothers watch Yell and the others as they depart.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あれから２週間、今度はヘルマンに向かった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Two weeks later, they head toward Helman.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いろいろな冒険の様子
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Scenes of various adventures.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: Ｒの紋章を使って道行く人に試してみたが出なかった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They tried using the R emblem on passersby, but it didn't appear.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 街道を移動中
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Moving along the highway.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 東ヘルマンに関する話題
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A topic regarding East Helman.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 反ランスの国、自分達を襲ったデフェンダーの母国
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The anti-Rance country, the motherland of the Defenders who attacked them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もし自分達がランスを倒したらどうなるのかな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What would happen if they defeated Rance?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスを元に戻しても彼らは納得しない、火だねは残る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if Rance is restored, they won't be satisfied; the spark of conflict remains.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンス、リアがわざと残している話
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The story that Zansu and Ria are deliberately leaving it unresolved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 西ヘルマン首都に到着
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arrival at West Helman capital.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 貧乏だけで温和な国、魔物界の一部も持っており、魔物、人間などで共存している。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A poor but peaceful country, partly part of the monster world, coexisting with monsters and humans.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シーラが大統領
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sheila is the president.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 貴方たちの話は聞いているわ、でも、ごめんなさい。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have heard your story, but I'm sorry.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ついレリコフにオーブの事を話てしまった、あの子ったらヒーロー君を連れて先に取ってくると
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I accidentally told Relikov about the orb; that kid took Hero-kun and went ahead to get it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 向かってしまったの・・　みんなが来てから一緒に行くべきなのに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They went... We should have gone together after everyone arrived.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 場所はシベリア、巨大戦艦内
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Location: Siberia, inside a giant battleship.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すごい寒いシベリアに来ます、始めて
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Coming to the very cold Siberia, for the first time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 目的を再確認
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reconfirming the objectives.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・レリコフ、ヒーローと会う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: - Meet with Relikov and Hero.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・巨大戦艦でオーブを取る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: - Retrieve the orb on the giant battleship.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 氷雪地帯を移動中、キャラバンを発見
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While traveling through the snowy region, they discover a caravan.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 少し寄ってみる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They stop by briefly.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 世界一と言われる移動型売春宿。有名です。高いので一般では利用出来ないが、サービス満点
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A mobile brothel said to be the best in the world. Famous and expensive, so not accessible to the general public, but offers excellent service.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここから少年達のエロ話になります。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: From here, it turns into an erotic story involving the boys.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンス　俺はそこで筆おろしをするつもりだったのだ、一緒にどうだとか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Zansu: I intended to lose my virginity there, inviting someone to join me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女性向けのサービスもあるらしいよ、最高のサービスでやさしく処女を捨てさせてくれんだって
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Apparently, they also have services for women, offering the best care to gently help them lose their virginity.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの子供達は、みんな童貞と処女
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance's children are all virgins, both boys and girls.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エールが男か女かで　ボーイズトークかガールズトーク
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Depending on whether Yell is male or female, it's boys' talk or girls' talk.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もちろん、今はいかない。立ち去ります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Of course, they don't go now. They leave.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シベリアを進んでいると・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As they advance through Siberia...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 向こうに誰かがいる、こっちに向かって走ってくる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Someone is over there, running toward them.
